c: 30
v: 8
t: "Vanombofungawo maererano ivo pachavo (nezvekusikwa kwavo here pasina kana chii zvacho, nekuti Allah vachazovamutsa)? Allah havana kusika matenga nenyika uye zviri mazviri kusara nechokwadi uye kwenguva yakatarwa. Asi zvirokwazvo vanhu vazhinji vanoramba kuti vachave vanosangana naTenzi vavo"